  "text": "Lung function tests. We measured standard spirometric values according to American Thoracic Society guidelines (American Thoracic Society 1991), and we used reference values of [CITATION_1] for the Finnish population. We recorded spirometric and peak expiratory flow (PEF) values during and after the exposures (Table 1) .",
